<tool id="dbbuilder_metabolites" name="Metabolite Database Downloader" version="0.0.1">

<description>A tool to download free metabolite spectral databases (using MSP / MSL format). <i>Examples:<\i> Fiehn db, Golm db, MONA db. <b>Caution:<\b> Every database uses a different data format, although all are equally called "MSP" or "MSL". Every format contains the same information, but uses a unique file structure. </description>

